{"tid":2293581,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"offer選擇","createTime":"2020-11-20T10:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T13:36:38.000Z","uid":165022,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"01a773e99fd794ed515805b1a53d71bbb9656eb6","tid":2293581,"uid":165022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"小弟有兩個offer想請教吓各位推薦邊份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟係2020fg, 番緊offer 1嗰份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOffer 1: MNC 25k, 15AL,穩定career path但係做緊自己唔鐘意做既野<br />\n<br />\nOffer 2: Local 16k, 12AL, career path比offer 1更好,而且係做一直想試既野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我自己係想試offer 2嗰份,但係offer 1做多大半年就會加到30k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然offer 2個career path比1好，但係要儲經驗，我驚追唔到offer 1個人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係同時offer 2間公司expand得好快，我有好多發揮既空間，而offer 1 MNC好多野都定晒形要跟規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7994d85d2ef1a61f58c1be2277f28ffffc0587","tid":2293581,"uid":34764,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:38:26.000Z","msg":"勁 今年fg就搵到25k 係讀工程畢業？？"},{"pid":"5f38fa51eb3480f3c4c8b603c97401f3f4a38cae","tid":2293581,"uid":184666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"咪問過囉，又再問過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bbc22470b04aac3ec9cb5e29b981988e2f570b","tid":2293581,"uid":165022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f38fa51eb3480f3c4c8b603c97401f3f4a38cae","tid":2293581,"uid":184666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"咪問過囉，又再問過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:40:28.000Z","msg":"Offer 2同上次唔同架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as